---
title: Harissa Sausage Naan Pizza with Roasted Pepper, Feta and Baby Gem Salad
description: Our harissa sausage naan pizza is the perfect midweek meal. Alongside the sausagemeat, the naan is filled with sweet yellow peppers, tangy feta cheese and a warm harissa & tomato base. Serve with a side of refreshing, crunchy baby gem for a satisfying dinner packed with tongue-tingling flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/harissa-sausage-naan-pizza-bb1e7449-ac48a408.jpg
